<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201024/68807da2435849dd9c8a28604009c502.jpeg" style="user-select: auto;" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">美女建筑师陈敏英用水给楼当镜子，</p>
<p>造出南京最文艺售楼处。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201024/fd60019106084c409e47ad2df3c822fe.jpeg" style="user-select: auto;" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
